You will need IPython, NumPy, SciPy, PyMC, Daft, and scikit-learn.

The best way to get this software is to install Anaconda [1].
You will need to separately run
 - pip install pymc
 - pip install daft

[1] https://store.continuum.io/cshop/anaconda/

Then in this directory, type
 - ipython notebook --pylab=inline

And go to 127.0.0.1:8888 in your browser. Enjoy!

